    <node id="Love For Odysseus">
      <data key="d0">Love For Odysseus</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Love for Odysseus is the obsessive affection attributed to Calypso, described as the reason for her suicide and her eternal yearning for his return.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-67499e7b6b869922afb829c43d6b368e</data>
