    <node id="Folly Of Obsession">
      <data key="d0">Folly Of Obsession</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Folly of obsession is a critical idea expressed in the poem "Calypso Watching the Ocean," commenting on the irrationality of Calypso's obsessive yearning for Odysseus.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-67499e7b6b869922afb829c43d6b368e</data>
      <data key="d4">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Calypso_(mythology)</data>
